column5: Well I awoke at 2 A:M. The world looks like it's still here, at least Hamilton is. Guess I'll be running around all day tomorrow, I'll have lots to do. After maxing out all my credit cards for the past 2 weeks in anticipation of the "Big Mayan Event" I will now have to return everything I bought 'cause I haven't the money to pay for it all!  Biggest problem will be returning the New Dodge Viper I picked up last week. Think the dealer will take it back? I think they may give me a little bit of trouble.

Oh boy !!!! You have some explaining to do at the insurance company !!! Haha.... Ya no end of the world.....  Now I gotta go outside and clean off all the freezing rain... We got it pretty good up here
That'll clean up just fine with some soap & water Harry
Its got December 21 2012 writen all over it , problaby worth a mint .
I guess I go to work today.
dont get too cocky just yet, theres still 15-1/2 hours left in the day.
I wonder if Tim Tomas knows that world hasn't ended.
